                        <interp inst="t18400406-name-476" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD HURCHINGS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 85.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the person who was then tried by the name of Newton.</p>
